              "free_text": [
                " Unable to obtain data from authors, digitized",
                "data."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The A=238 mass chain evaluation has slightly",
                "different, within a decimal point, energy levels.",
                "EXFOR compilation level energies are based on the",
                "data that were in experimental paper. Gamma rays",
                "detected indicate energy levels, however, feeding",
                "from the higher lying states was not excluded."
              ]
            }
          ],
